# SHAPES

Vector            V
Pencil            P
Line              L
Rect              R
Oval              O
Rounded           U
Text              T
Artboard          A
Slice             S


# ZOOM

Zoom              Z
Reverse Zoom      Alt + Z
Zoom In           Cmd + +
Zoom Out          Cmd + -
Actual Size       Cmd + 0
Center Canvas     Cmd + 1
Zoom Selection    Cmd + 2
Center Selection  Cmd + 3
Drag Viewport     Space + Mouse-Drag


# View Toggles

Pixels            Ctl + P
Rulers            Ctl + R
Grid              Ctl + G
Select Handles    Ctl + H
Distance Guides   Ctl + L


# Layers

