Rotate            Shf + Cmd + T


# Arrange

Forward           Alt + Cmd + Up
Front             Ctl + Alt + Cmd + Up
Backward          Alt + Cmd + Down
Back              Ctl + Alt + Cmd + Down
Group             Cmd + G
Group             Shf + Cmd + G
Hide              Shf + Cmd + H
Lock              Shf + Cmd + L
Rename            Cmd + R
